&lt;p&gt;This role will lead packaging design and illustration across core launches and IP collaborations, while driving retail efforts including in-store displays and branded environments. Beyond retail, the Senior Designer will shape the brand across our DTC website, lifecycle marketing, and more — ensuring a cohesive and unmistakable presence everywhere we show up.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Working cross-functionally with Marketing and Product, this role will bring concepts to life through systemic artwork development, production-ready execution, color matching, and press checks.&lt;/p&gt;
