&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Concept and develop innovative design solutions across packaging, retail, digital, and print touchpoints — applying strong hierarchy, systems thinking, typography, and bold visual storytelling.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead artwork development from concept through production in partnership with internal teams and external supply chain vendors.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own packaging and retail execution including QA

